title: Ep. 376 - Biden Babbles And Warren Lies
description:
We'll analyze a mostly boring debate, aside from a few hilarious moments from Joe Biden. Elizabeth Warren told an absurd lie about her tax plan. We'll discuss the reality of it. Also, with schools allowing boys into girls locker rooms, one big question must be asked: why are parents still sending their daughters to these schools? When are we as parents going to stand up and fight back? Date: 11-21-2019
